data.title: واکنش رامبد جوان به بی ادبی برخی کاربران ایرانی - به یاد ماندنی
data.meta_description:
Rambod Javan born on 22 December 1971 in Shahrara. is an Iranian actor, director, TV host and is the author of many screenplays. Rambod Javan has made and directed a locally famous TV program, Khandevane. Wikipedia
Born: December 22, 1971 (age 45), Tehran
Height: 1.76 m
Education: Islamic Azad University
Spouse: Negar Javaherian (m. 2014), Sahar Dolatshahi (m. 2009–2014)
Nominations: Crystal Simor
